The Eurotech SensorTag application is based on the TI SensorTag app that can be found here: https://git.ti.com/sensortag-20-android

New features:
  * support to EDC
  * luxometer tab
  * Eurotech and EDC logos

Known issues:
  * when a cloud configuration is set and the configuration panel is opened, the fields are empty.
  * sometimes, when the sensors tab is opened, the list is empty
  * sometimes the service discovery fails.